headline: Jack Henry & Associates Increases the Quarterly Dividend on its Common Stock by 6 Percent to $.61 Per Share
summary: Jack Henry & Associates, Inc. (NASDAQ: JKHY) today announced its Board of Directors increased the quarterly dividend by six percent (6%) to $.61 per share. The cash dividend on its common stock, par value $.01 per share, is payable on March 25, 2026, to stockholders of record as of March 5, 2026. Jack Henry has paid consecutive quarterly dividends since 1991, and 2025 marked the 22nd consecutive year of an increasing dividend.
